sentences: In 1996 he founded Akashic Books out of Brooklyn with the intent of publishing works by independent artists.
It was during his second year that Temple began playing bass guitar, with much of his influence being drawn from the punk rock and reggae scene in D.C.
Johnny Temple married in 2002 and has two sons.
He has lived in Fort Greene, Brooklyn since 1990 and told The New York Times that one of his "goals in life is to leave Fort Greene as little as possible".
